728589f-a.title: Richmond: Bell Street - Reynolds Street
728589f-a.text:
Bell Street (right, children thereon), east from Reynolds Street
(Rosebank). Also shown are the tracks of the Staten Island Railroad.
Bell Street was formerly Wall Street.
July 12, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
728589f-a.folder: Bell Street & Reynolds Street, Staten Island, NY

728588f-b.title: Richmond: Bell Street - Reynolds Street
728588f-b.text:
(1)
84 Bell Street, adjoining the S.W. corner of Reynolds Street
(Rosebank). P. L. Sperr states that it is the residence of Mrs.
J.. McCarthy. Bell Street was formerly Wall Street.
July 12, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
Part of the same, showing the west edge of the house.
July 12, 1934.
P. 1L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

729296f-a.title: Richmond: Reynolds Street - Bell Street
729296f-a.text:
Reynolds Street, east side, south from Bell Street
to St. Marys Avenue.
July 12, 1934
P. L. Soerr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
